      <title>Booking 首席财务官称通胀影响仍在抑制美国旅游需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/booking-cfo-says-inflation-impact-still-curbing-us-travel-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Booking Holdings Inc. 表示，通货膨胀的影响仍然抑制美国的旅游需求，注重价格的消费者需要等待更长时间来计划假期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/booking-cfo-says-inflation-impact-still-curbing-us-travel-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
